Exhaustive analysis at n=5 (1024 tournaments)
======================================================================

Approach 1: Does adjacent dominated cycle always have |dom|>=2?
  b1=0 with free cycles: 240
  has (F adj D with |dom(D)|>=2): 0
  only single-dom: 240
  If has_multidom covers all: guaranteed n-4=1 good vertices

Approach 2: When single-dom, is d in V(F)?
  d in V(F): 0 (gives n-4=1 good)
  d not in V(F): 480 (gives n-5=0 good)

Approach 3: Best (F,D) pair analysis
  min best_good: 0
  distribution: {0: 240}

